                        "description": "Spectra were processed using MestReNova v9.0 program. The signals from interpritated metabolites were integrated,  Several multiplets in an NMR spectrum can correspond to the same substance. To improve the quantification accuracy for low-concentrated metabolites, the sum of the integrated intensities of such multiplets was used whenever possible. However, if 1 or more of the multiplets fell in the overcrowded regions of an NMR spectrum and overlapped with signals corresponding to other substances, only a single non-overlapping multiplet was used for quantification. All integrals were normalized to total sum of all integrals.",
